{"tid":1285483,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[七月新番] 致曾為神之眾獸","createTime":"2019-07-04T15:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T08:31:09.000Z","uid":402,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9ad0fc525d584ce7bb9c7a3f6fcefb026594c3fc","tid":1285483,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6bKS9x4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6bKS9x4.jpg&h=16b2e9ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為了終結持續不斷的內戰而製造出來的擬神兵，終於替國家帶來了和平，成為英雄。但在戰爭結束後，他們卻墮落為野獸，並不斷遭到獵獸者的追殺。少女夏爾的爸爸也被獵獸者殺死，因此決定找獵獸者報仇。然而實際認識了獵獸者漢克，並與他一同踏上獵殺擬神兵的旅程之後，夏爾才發現他的真實身分，與潛藏在其內心那不為人知的苦衷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n原作：めいびい<br />\n監督：宍戸淳<br />\n系列構成：村越繁<br />\n角色設計・總作畫監督：新沼大祐<br />\n擬神兵設計監修：佐野誉幸<br />\n色彩設計：鎌田千賀子<br />\n美術監督：森川裕史<br />\n撮影監督：三舟桃子<br />\n編集：相原聡<br />\n動畫製作：MAPPA<br />\n <br />\nCAST<br />\n漢克：小西克幸<br />\n夏爾：加隈亜衣<br />\n<br />\n官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://katsu-kami.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkatsu-kami.com%2F&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=2d2bd407\" target=\"_blank\">https://katsu-kami.com/</a>"},{"pid":"49b6d50fc5fd89c07610b746b803f009c78898d6","tid":1285483,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:02:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://anime1.me/?cat=550\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanime1.me%2F%3Fcat%3D550&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRT11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=32ab3dbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://anime1.me/?cat=550</a>"},{"pid":"c4654a12e54c73f14e5eeea7343958ba616870ef","tid":1285483,"uid":134665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:02:18.000Z","msg":"幫你推下"},{"pid":"afb92439858b04fff465c71190162322c37a4ea8","tid":1285483,"uid":402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:02:26.000Z","msg":"竟然無人開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6346f5162c